      "message": "This needs a bit of color space logic:\n\nif (!dstInfo.colorSpace()):\n  // What you wrote works perfect.  We will do a legacy draw, which is all we can do without a color space\nelse if (dstInfo.colorSpace() \u0026\u0026 kRespect \u003d\u003d options.fPremulBehavior):\n  // What you wrote works perfect.  We will do a color correct draw because the canvas has a color space\nelse:   // dstInfo.colorSpace() \u0026\u0026 kIgnore\n  // We want a legacy draw that preconverts to the dst color space\n  auto xformCanvas \u003d SkCreateColorSpaceXformCanvas(legacyCanvas, dstInfo.colorSpace());\n  // Draw to the xform canvas",
